bad management decisions that you would like to comment on?

Dr.  FAINBERG.  Well,  Congressman,  sympathetic  to  where  you
come  from,  I  grew  up  in  Hackensack  and  my  parents  are  still
there.

hand.

Mr. ROTHMAN. My constituents.
