Chairman  MILLER.  Thank  you,  Admiral  Cohen.  I  am  delighted
that  you  were  able  to  use  the  easels  that  you  brought  here  this
morning.

[Whereupon, at 1:05 p.m., the Subcommittee was adjourned.]

